 to millions of people: Pluto TV viewers, partners and soon everyone on the planet.\"},{\"index\":\"04\",\"title\":\"Own Your Sh*t\",\"text\":\"Not only do we take the initiative and lead, but we hold ourselves and each other accountable.\"},{\"index\":\"02\",\"title\":\"Challenge and Commit\",\"text\":\"Our curiosity compels us to challenge what we know, or think we know, in order to make better decisions. Once we commit, we align completely to deliver the results.\"},{\"index\":\"05\",\"title\":\"Do More With less\",\"text\":\"Our time, focus and expertise is invaluable. We prioritize how to maximize our biggest impact while using the least amount of resources.\"},{\"index\":\"03\",\"title\":\"Warp Speed, Mr. Sulu\",\"text\":\"Fortune favors the fast. Our warp speed allows us to reach goals before our competition, and to answer our viewers\' needs before they know they have them.\"},{\"index\":\"06\",\"title\":\"Be Pluto\",\"text\":\"Like our namesake planet, our underdog status motivates us: to move faster, think bigger, and work harder than our competition. Together, we\'ll beat the odds.\"}],\"perks_list_1\":[\"Medical, dental and vision\",\"Life insurance\",\"Flexible spending accounts\",\"Employee assistance program\",\"401K retirement plan\"],\"perks_list_2\":[\"Flexible vacation opportunities\",\"Discounted gym membership\",\"Parking and commuter benefits\",\"Social events, company parties and frequent happy hours\",\"Catered breakfasts, holiday treats and 24/7 snacks\"],\"benefits_package\":\"Our benefits package\",\"browse_careers\":\"Browse Careers\",\"partners_hero_title\":\"Be part of our world.\",\"partner_with_leading\":\"Partner with the leading free streaming TV service in America.\",\"put_pluto_on_device\":\"Put Pluto TV on your device\",\"our_mission_entertain\":\"Our mission is to entertain the planet, which means working with the best content creators in the world and distributing their work across the best devices out there.\",\"partner_with_u